author: cnbc.com
title: Rayonier Scheduled to Release First Quarter Earnings on May 2
text:
YULEE, Fla.--(BUSINESS WIRE)-- Rayonier Inc. (NYSE:RYN) plans to release its first quarter 2018 earnings after the market closes on Wednesday, May 2, 2018.
Rayonier will host a conference call and live audio webcast at 10:00 a.m. (EDT) on Thursday, May 3, 2018 to discuss these results. Supplemental materials and access to the live audio webcast will be available at www.rayonier.com . A replay of the webcast will be archived on the Companyâ€™s website and available shortly after the call.
Investors may listen to the conference call by dialing 800-369-1184 (domestic) or 415-228-3898 (international), passcode: Rayonier. A replay of the conference call will be available one hour following the call until Thursday, May 10, 2018, by dialing 866-495-6518 (domestic) or 203-369-1770 (international), passcode: 4032018.
About Rayonier
Rayonier is a leading timberland real estate investment trust with assets located in some of the most productive softwood timber growing regions in the United States and New Zealand. As of December 31, 2017, Rayonier owned, leased or managed approximately 2.6 million acres of timberlands located in the U.S. South (1.8 million acres), U.S. Pacific Northwest (378,000 acres) and New Zealand (410,000 acres). More information is available at www.rayonier.com .
